    <!-- Visualization & Content Choices: 
        1. Report Info: Chronotype comparison (Table 1). Goal: Compare. Viz: Interactive Bar Chart (Chart.js). Interaction: Hover for details. Justification: More engaging and visually clearer than a static table for comparing two distinct profiles.
        2. Report Info: Daytime drain/nighttime surge feedback loop. Goal: Show Relationship. Viz: Custom HTML/CSS diagram. Interaction: Clickable hotspots to reveal detailed text. Justification: Visually explains the complex feedback loop in a simple, intuitive way that text alone cannot.
        3. Report Info: Daily habits for optimization (Table 3). Goal: Organize/Inform. Viz: Interactive checklist/cards. Interaction: Click to select and add to a personalized plan. Justification: Turns passive information into an active tool, empowering the user to make choices and see a tangible output, which boosts motivation.
    -->
